    <section id="about">
        <h2>About TechConnect</h2>
        <p>TechConnect was inspired by the growing need for efficient backend solutions in modern web development. Our journey began with a vision to streamline the development process and empower developers to focus on building innovative frontend experiences.</p>
        <p>Developed as a Portfolio Project for Holberton School, TechConnect aims to accelerate time-to-market and enhance user experiences, ultimately benefiting developers and businesses alike.</p>
